- [NEW] MEDIA TOOLS PANEL — BLUEPRINT
Purpose: One unified workspace with previews for:

1. Image Tools
- Resize (720p, 1080p, custom WxH)
- Convert format (PNG → JPG, WEBP, AVIF)
- Compress (quality slider)
- Filters (blur, sharpen, denoise, monochrome, sepia)

2. Video Tools
- Resize (720p, 1080p, custom WxH)
- Re-encode (H264 / HEVC / VP9 / AV1)
- Trim (start, end)
- Change FPS
- Compress bitrate

3. Audio Tools
- Convert (MP3 / OGG / WAV / FLAC)
- Bitrate control
- Trim
- Normalize volume

4. Target Media Picker
- Auto-populated from selected table:
- Playfield image/video
- Backglass image/video
- DMD image/video
- Topper image/video
- Wheel image
- Table music
- Launch audio

5. Requirements: 
- be able to manipulate single table, selection of table, all tables
- use ffmpeg/imagemagick
- be able to manipulate single or selection of media. e.g:
    - only dmd all tables
    - dmd and topper for selection of tables
    - all images for all tables etc
